        <h2>2.Lists</h2>
            <h3>2.1 Unordered List</h3>
            <u1>
                 <1i>Apple</1i>
                 <1i>Banana</1i>
                 <1i>Orange</1i>
            </u1>
            <h4>2.2 Ordered List</h4>
            <o1>
                <1i>Apple</1i>
                <1i>Banana</1i>
                <1i>Orange</1i>
            </o1>
       <h2>3.Formatting Text Inline</h2>
           <h3>3.1 To bold some text. </h3>
               <p>The bolded text is used to <strong>draw your attention</strong></p>
           <h3>3.2 Other commomly used tags for formatting text inline </h3>
           <u1>
               <1i>To itaticize text:<em>This is italics text</em></1i>
               <1i>To underline text:<u>This is underlined text</u></1i>
               <1i>To cross out text:<s>This is crossed out text </s></1i>
               <1i>To highlight text:<mark>This is higlighted text</mark></1i>
               <1i>Create line break:<br> This sentences<br>contains<br>several lines.</l1>
           </u1>

